w-7 items-center justify-center rounded-md bg-primary text-primary-foreground text-xs font-black\">AF</span><span class=\"hidden sm:inline\">AlgoForge</span></a><nav class=\"hidden lg:flex items-center gap-1\" aria-label=\"Main\"><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/problems\">Problems</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/topics\">Topics</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/patterns\">Patterns</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/roadmaps\">Roadmaps</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/blind-75\">Blind 75</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/companies\">Companies</a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground hover:bg-muted transition-colors\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a></nav></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"hidden sm:inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card px-3 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:border-primary/40 transition-colors\" href=\"/search\"><span>Search…</span><kbd class=\"rounded border border-border bg-muted px-1.5 text-[10px] font-mono\">/</kbd></a><a class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/dashboard\">Progress</a><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 hover:bg-muted text-foreground h-9 w-9\" aria-label=\"Toggle theme\"></button></div></div></header><main id=\"main\" class=\"min-h-[70vh]\"><div class=\"container-af py-10\"><nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Problems\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/problems\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Design Memory Allocator\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/problems/design-memory-allocator\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":4,\"name\":\"C++\",\"item\":\"https://algoforge.dev/problems/design-memory-allocator/cpp\"}]}</script><ol class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center gap-1.5\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"text-border\">/</span><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/problems\">Problems</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"text-border\">/</span><a class=\"hover:text-primary transition-colors\" href=\"/problems/design-memory-allocator\">Design Memory Allocator</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1.5\"><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"text-border\">/</span><span class=\"text-foreground font-medium\" aria-current=\"page\">C++</span></li></ol></nav><div class=\"mt-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full px-2.5 py-0.5 text-xs font-semibold tracking-wide bg-medium/15 text-medium\">Medium</span></div><h1 class=\"mt-3 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Design Memory Allocator<!-- --> — <!-- -->C++</h1><p class=\"mt-2 text-muted-foreground\"><a class=\"text-primary hover:underline\" href=\"/problems/design-memory-allocator\">Full explanation</a> · <!-- -->Time <!-- -->ctor: O(1) allocate: O(logn) free: O(logn)<!-- --> · Space <!-- -->O(n)</p><div class=\"mt-8\"><div class=\"rounded-xl border border-border overflow-hidden bg-code-bg text-slate-100\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap items-center justify-between gap-2 border-b border-white/10 bg-black/30 px-2 py-1.5\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-1\" role=\"tablist\" aria-label=\"Language\"><button role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"true\" class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium transition-colors bg-white/15 text-white\">C++</button><button role=\"tab\" aria-selected=\"false\" class=\"rounded-md px-2.5 py-1 text-xs font-medium transition-colors text-slate-400 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/5\">Python</button></div><button class=\"inline-flex items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-ring disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 px-3 text-sm text-slate-300 hover:text-white hover:bg-white/10 h-8\" type=\"button\" aria-label=\"Copy code\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-copy h-3.5 w-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect width=\"14\" height=\"14\" x=\"8\" y=\"8\" rx=\"2\" ry=\"2\"></rect><path d=\"M4 16c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V4c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h10c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2\"></path></svg>Copy</button></div><pre class=\"overflow-x-auto p-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed font-mono max-h-[32rem]\"><code>// Time:  ctor:     O(1)\n//        allocate: O(logn)\n//        free:     O(logn)\n// Space: O(n)\n\n// bst\nclass Allocator {\npublic:\n    Allocator(int n) : avails_{{0, n}} {\n    }\n    \n    int allocate(int size, int mID) {\n        for (const auto [l, s] : avails_) {\n            if (s &lt; size) {\n                continue;\n            }\n            avails_.erase(l);\n            lookup_[mID].emplace_back(l, size);\n            if (s - size &gt; 0) {\n                avails_.emplace(l + size, s - size);\n            }\n            return l;\n        }\n        return -1;\n    }\n    \n    int free(int mID) {\n        if (!lookup_.count(mID)) {\n            return 0;\n        }\n        int result = 0;\n        for (const auto&amp; [l, s] : lookup_[mID]) {\n            auto it = avails_.emplace(l, s).first;\n            if (next(it) != end(avails_) &amp;&amp; it-&gt;first + it-&gt;second == next(it)-&gt;first) {\n                it-&gt;second += next(it)-&gt;second;\n                avails_.erase(next(it));\n            }\n            if (it != begin(avails_) &amp;&amp; prev(it)-&gt;first + prev(it)-&gt;second == it-&gt;first) {\n                prev(it)-&gt;second += it-&gt;second;\n                avails_.erase(it);\n            }\n            result += s;\n        }\n        lookup_.erase(mID);\n        return result;\n    }\n\nprivate:\n    map&lt;int, int&gt; avails_;\n    unordered_map&lt;int, vector&lt;pair&lt;int, int&gt;&gt;&gt; lookup_;\n};\n</code></pre></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"mt-20 border-t border-border bg-sidebar\"><div class=\"container-af py-12 grid gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4\"><div><p class=\"font-bold text-lg\">AlgoForge</p><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground max-w-xs\">Master coding interviews with patterns, roadmaps, and solutions</p></div><div><p class=\"font-semibold text-sm mb-3\">Learn</p><ul class=\"space-y-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/problems\">Problems</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/patterns\">Patterns</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/roadmaps\">Roadmaps</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/blind-75\">Blind 75</a></li><li><a class=\"hover:text-primary\" href=\"/grind-169\">Grind 169</a></li></ul></div><div>